 137:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_ll_usb.c ****   /* The USBTRD is configured according to the tables below, depending on AHB frequency
 138:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_ll_usb.c ****   used by application. In the low AHB frequency range it is used to stretch enough the USB response
 139:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_ll_usb.c ****   time to IN tokens, the USB turnaround time, so to compensate for the longer AHB read access
 140:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_ll_usb.c ****   latency to the Data FIFO */
 141:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_ll_usb.c ****   if (speed == USBD_FS_SPEED)
